    },
    {
      "actor": "Rin",
      "name": "Everything feels… stuck.",
      "dialogType": "Normal",
      "translates": [
        {
          "lang": "ru-RU",
          "name": ""
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "actor": "Lumo",
      "name": "Because it had been happening for too long.",
      "dialogType": "Normal",
      "translates": [
        {
          "lang": "ru-RU",
          "name": ""
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "actor": "Rin",
      "name": "So this is stronger than just saying: 'It was happening'?",
      "dialogType": "Normal",
      "translates": [
        {
          "lang": "ru-RU",
          "name": ""
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "actor": "Lumo",
      "name": "Yes. 'Was happening' is Past Continuous. It focuses on the moment.",
      "dialogType": "Normal",
      "translates": [
        {
          "lang": "ru-RU",
          "name": ""
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "actor": "Rin",
      "name": "And Past Perfect is about what had happened.",
      "dialogType": "Normal",
      "translates": [
        {
          "lang": "ru-RU",
          "name": ""
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "actor": "Lumo",
      "name": "But Past Perfect Continuous shows **how long** it had been happening.",
      "dialogType": "Normal",
      "translates": [
        {
          "lang": "ru-RU",
          "name": ""
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "actor": "Rin",
      "name": "Like: I had been crying for hours before help came.",
      "dialogType": "Normal",
      "translates": [
        {
          "lang": "ru-RU",
          "name": ""
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "actor": "Lumo",
      "name": "Exactly. It’s the **duration** before another past event.",
      "dialogType": "Normal",
      "translates": [
        {
          "lang": "ru-RU",
          "name": ""
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "actor": "Rin",
      "name": "She had been working since sunrise when the call arrived.",
      "dialogType": "Normal",
      "translates": [
        {
          "lang": "ru-RU",
          "name": ""
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "actor": "Lumo",
      "name": "Perfect. Now let's test your understanding.",
      "dialogType": "Normal",
      "translates": [
        {
          "lang": "ru-RU",
          "name": ""
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "actor": "Lumo",
      "name": "Which sentence shows duration before something else?",
      "dialogType": "Normal",
      "translates": [
        {
          "lang": "ru-RU",
          "name": "Какое предложение показывает длительность до события?"
        }
      ],
      "actions": [
        {
          "name": "He had been waiting since morning before the train arrived.",
          "isCorrect": true,
          "score": 1
        },
        {
          "name": "He waited since morning before the train arrives.",
          "isCorrect": false,
          "score": 0
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "actor": "Lumo",
      "name": "Write a sentence with: had been, working, since",
      "dialogType": "Write",
      "translates": [
        {
          "lang": "ru-RU",
          "name": "Составь предложение с had been, working, since"
        }
      ],
      "actions": [
        {
          "name": "She had been working since dawn before the lights went out.",
          "isCorrect": true,
          "score": 1
        },
        {
          "name": "She work since dawn before lights go out.",
          "isCorrect": false,
          "score": 0
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "actor": "Rin",
      "name": "So it’s not just what happened, but how long it had been happening.",
      "dialogType": "Normal",
      "translates": [
        {
          "lang": "ru-RU",
          "name": ""
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "actor": "Lumo",
      "name": "Exactly. That’s the core of this tense.",
      "dialogType": "Normal",
      "translates": [
        {
          "lang": "ru-RU",
          "name": ""
        }
      ]
    }
  ]
